p.d: The world may know them as Wonder Woman, Supergirl and Batgirl, but as not-so-typical teenagers, they have much more to deal with than just protecting the citizens of Metropolis. After all, being teens is tough enough. But add super powers and a secret identity to the mix and things can get a lot more complicated!
